{"title":"槐树下","authors":["刘兰松"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"槐树下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘兰松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭上河，日西挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂们坐在槐树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手上的银针闪闪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳着鞋底学宪法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辅导员，小翠花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话响嘎嘎："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总任务好象那明灯照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新宪法就是托灯的塔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政要巩固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民心里乐开花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张大嫂，接话茬："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新宪法说出咱心里话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“牛二拐”他敢再奓刺儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他牛角劈半拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李二嫂，把言发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口口声声把二哥夸："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺那口子如今干活气死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不怪话连天闲磨牙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小山丫，抢话把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人面前把二嫂“刮”："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与二哥学宪法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺在门缝看见啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二嫂只顾抿嘴乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不小心针把手指扎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭上河，日西挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂们树下学宪法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞋底纳得似铁板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“长征”路上大步跨……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}